## Data Loading

directorytr = "/kaggle/input/cs412-spring-2021/train_data/train"
IMSIZE= 224
target_size = (IMSIZE,IMSIZE)
BS = 256
seed = 0
save_to_dir = None
data_generator = ImageDataGenerator(validation_split=0.2, 
                                    dtype=np.float32,
                                    rescale=1./255)
## Generator Defintions
def initialize_generators():
    train_generator = data_generator.flow_from_directory(
        directorytr,
        target_size=target_size,
        color_mode="rgb",
        classes=None,
        class_mode="categorical",
        batch_size=BS,
        shuffle=True,
        seed=seed,
        save_to_dir=save_to_dir,
        save_prefix="",
        save_format="png",
        subset="training",
        interpolation="nearest",
    )
    val_generator = train_generator = data_generator.flow_from_directory(
        directorytr,
        target_size=target_size,
        color_mode="rgb",
        classes=None,
        class_mode="categorical",
        batch_size=BS,
        shuffle=True,
        seed=seed,
        save_to_dir=save_to_dir,
        save_prefix="",
        save_format="png",
        subset="validation",
        interpolation="nearest",
    )
    return train_generator, val_generator

In [10]:
# Model Definition

def get_model():
    
    initializer = 'he_uniform'
    num_class = 29
    
    # Pretrained infrastructure
    base = MobileNetV2(weights='imagenet', include_top=False, input_shape=(IMSIZE,IMSIZE,3))
    base.trainable=False
    
    model = Sequential()
    
    model.add(base)
    
    
    model.add(GlobalAveragePooling2D())
        
    model.add(Dense(units = 128,
                    activation = 'relu',
                    kernel_initializer = initializer, 
                    kernel_regularizer=regularizers.l1_l2(l1=1e-5, l2=1e-4),
                    bias_regularizer=regularizers.l2(1e-4),
                    activity_regularizer=regularizers.l2(1e-5)))
    model.add(Dropout(0.2))
    
    model.add(Dense(units = 64,
                    activation = 'relu',
                    kernel_initializer = initializer, 
                    kernel_regularizer=regularizers.l1_l2(l1=1e-5, l2=1e-4),
                    bias_regularizer=regularizers.l2(1e-4),
                    activity_regularizer=regularizers.l2(1e-5)))
    model.add(Dropout(0.2))

    model.add(Dense(units = num_class,
                    activation = 'softmax', 
                    kernel_initializer=initializer))

    return model

In [14]:
# Refresh data
tr_generator, val_generator = initialize_generators()

# Train the model

early_stopping = keras.callbacks.EarlyStopping(monitor = 'val_accuracy', patience = 4, verbose=True, 
                                               restore_best_weights=True,
                                               min_delta=0.001)
reduce_lr = keras.callbacks.ReduceLROnPlateau(monitor = 'val_loss', factor = 0.05, patience = 3, verbose=True,
                                            min_lr=1e-7)
callbacks = [early_stopping, reduce_lr]
history = model.fit(tr_generator,
                              steps_per_epoch = tr_generator.samples / BS,
                              validation_data = val_generator,
                              validation_steps = val_generator.samples / BS, 
                              epochs = 100,
                              callbacks = callbacks,
                              verbose = True
                              )
